Entering the Northern realm of the great Wizard, Sative of the Arcdiom, Jesse could feel the magical energy in the air all around.  He would seek this heralded Wizard to request an incantation allowing him to become a Life Sprit.  A Life Spirit was a form of living dead, this allowed people to seek answers in the world of the demons and gods.  Very few ever attempted this and fewer still lived.  To fail would result in becoming a minion to one of the demons of the underwold.<br>
<br>
